Supported Genomes

Source: R/supportedGenomes.R
supportedGenomes.Rd

Lists supported genomes

Usage

supportedGenomes()

Value

A data.frame containing supported genomes.

Details

Uses the ucscGenomes() function from the rtracklayer package to obtain a list of genomes available from the UCSC genome browser. The db column lists genomes as they are provided to the genome arguement of various functions.

The final column, headed AvailableGeneIDs lists the gene ID formats for which there is a local copy of the length information avaible for the genome listed in the geneLenDataBase package.

Author

Matthew D. Young myoung@wehi.edu.au
